run_metric_category(25.10)                          run_metric_category(25.10)

Name
       run_metric_category - Runs the specified category

Syntax
       run_metric_category

       [-help]

       -category<category_name>

       Runs the specified category.

Parameters
       -help  Describes the command usage.

       -category< category_name>
              Specifies the name of the category, such as design, setup, hold,
              clock, power, route, check, flow, to be run.

              Each category updates the metric associated with that category.

              Data_types: string, optional

